+\subsection{E. Maillet}
+\[(a+b)^3+(a+c)^3+(a+d)^3+(a-b)^3+(a-c)^3+(a-d)^3 = 6a(a^2+b^2+c^2+d^2)\]
+\begin{chunk}{*} 
+--S 1 of 63
+t1a:=(a+b)^3 + (a+c)^3 + (a+d)^3 + (a-b)^3 + (a-c)^3 + (a-d)^3
+--R 
