+\end{chunk}
+And we test combining the terms using the bitlist function call.
+\begin{chunk}{*}
+--S 39 of 63
+map(x+->factor(term(1,x)),bitlist(1))
+--R 
+--R
+--R   (39)  []
+--R                                       Type: List Factored Polynomial Integer
+--E 39
