+--R                        3                 3                 3               3
+--R   (41)  [(x  - x  - x ) ,- (x  - x  + x ) ,- (x  + x  - x ) ,(x  + x  + x ) ]
+--R            3    2    1       3    2    1       3    2    1     3    2    1
+--R                                       Type: List Factored Polynomial Integer
+--E 41
